rows.label: qev035403_MSG0002
rows.name: H-hey! You're the one working for Quincy![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev035403_MSG0003
rows.name:
Please,[ST:gender p1= man p2= lady ], you gotta help me! You just gotta!
The boys and I had us eggs for breakfast today,
and now mommy dearest here ain't happy about it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev035403_MSG0004
rows.name:
She's already eaten my boys, and now I'm clean
outta ammo. I'm in real bad shape here![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev035403_MSG0005
rows.name:
C'mon, we're both BLADEs, right? So help me!
Do it for the bond that daisy-headed idiot Quincy's
always yammering on about![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev035403_SEL0011
rows.name: Face the indigen in order to keep Gus alive.

rows.label: qev035403_SEL0021
rows.name: Leave Gus to the fate he has earned.

rows.label: qev035403_MSG0006
rows.name:
Aw, thanks, champ! I owe you big! HUGE!
Look, I'll cover your back while you work, okay?
You just take that thing out![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev035403_MSG0007
rows.name:
Well, screw you and the Skell you rode in on, pal!
And take a number, 'cause you're next in line as soon
as I kill this thing![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev035403_MSG0008
rows.name:
I ain't letting nobody at that Crimson Tear.
It's mine, do ya hear? MINE![ST:wait ]
